Usage: query_objects [-help] <collection> [-limit <value>]

-help            # Prints out the command usage
<collection>     # Specifies the object collection for which to return names.
                 # (string, required)
-limit <value>   # Specifies the maximum number of object names to return.
                 # Specify a value of 0 to return the names of all of the
                 # objects in the collection. {Default=100} (int, optional)